name: edgeworker_errorcode
sql:
(edgeworker_errorcode) -> multiIf (
  edgeworker_errorcode = '0',
  'unspecified',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '1',
  'success - EdgeWorkers function executed successfully',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '2',
  'genericError - Unnamed or uncategorized error',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '3',
  'unknownEdgeWorker - Unknown EdgeWorker ID',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '4',
  'unimplementedHandler - Requested event handler not implemented by EdgeWorkers function',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '5',
  'runtimeError - Error at runtime or environment prevented EdgeWorkers execution',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '6',
  'executionError - Error during EdgeWorkers execution, such as JavaScript exception or error',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '7',
  'timeoutError - EdgeWorkers timed out',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '8',
  'resourceLimit - EdgeWorkers hit preset resource limit',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '9',
  'ringBufferError - Error receiving or sending data through RingBuffer',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '10',
  'blacklisted - EdgeWorkers function is blacklisted by Akamai JavaScript execution engine',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '11',
  'bundleVersionUnavailable - EdgeWorkers code bundle unavailable for a particular version',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '12',
  'cpuTimeoutError - JavaScript exec CPU timed out',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '13',
  'wallTimeoutError - JavaScript exec Wall timed out',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '14',
  'initCpuTimeoutError - Init CPU timed out',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '15',
  'initWallTimeoutError - Init Wall timed out',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '16',
  'responseProviderCancelled - RP cancelled',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '17',
  'unsupportedResponseProviderMethod - responseProvider is attempting to run a method other than GET',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '18',
  'EdgeWorker deleted - EdgeWorkers function deleted by user',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '19',
  'softwareTooOld - Software too old',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '20',
  'erpDrop - Request dropped due to ERP',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '21',
  'Error discovered by the Akamai edge server',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '22',
  'subWorker not enabled',
  edgeworker_errorcode = '23',
  'subWorker limit hit',
  edgeworker_errorcode
)
